tornado/httputil.py
==================
889e1f3;Ben Darnell;2015-01-11 13:50:58 -0500;Correct handling of HTTP version numbers.
Per RFC 7230 section 2.6, we always output HTTP/1.1 even if the
request was HTTP/1.0 (and we accept any 1.x version).

