website/sphinx/releases/next.rst
==================
9df2324;Ben Darnell;2013-01-26 15:43:01 -0500;Use httputil.HTTPHeaders for outgoing headers in RequestHandler.
It's still a bit slower, but less than the 10% noted in the old comment.
